# summary of classes taken
classes <- background %>%
  select(11:29) %>%
  mutate_all(~factor(.x, levels = c('no', 'yes'))) %>%
  mutate_all(~as.numeric(.x) - 1) %>%
  summarize_all(mean) %>%
  gather(class, proportion)
